graph TD
    A[Raw Documentation Text<br/><small>layer_id, description</small>]
    A --> B{Sentence Splitter<br/>max_sentences=3}
    B --> C[Text Chunks<br/>with layer_id]
    C --> D{OpenAI Text Embedder<br/>text-embedding-3-small}
    D --> E[1536-dim Vector<br/>Embeddings]
    E --> F[Chunks + Embeddings<br/>+ layer_id]
    F --> G{PostgreSQL INSERT}
    G --> H[(Vector Database<br/>PostgreSQL + pgvector)]
    
    style B fill:#e3f2fd
    style D fill:#e3f2fd
    style G fill:#e3f2fd
    style H fill:#f5f5f5